quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  35,27,"Ur twalav ara Öebbi Isse$li d aman seg igenni? Nessuffe$ ed, yissen, ppemôa n yal ini. Deg idurar, isôiden icebêanen, izegwa$en n yal ini, akked iberkanen mavi"
  35,28,"Imdanen, lewêuc, lmal, n yal ini ula d nitni. Akka, ger imdanen iS, d imusnawen kan i ippagwaden Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Uzmir, Ipsemmiê"
  35,29,"Ih, wid iqqaôen Tazmamt n Öebbi, ipéallan, ipseddiqen seg wayen iten N$at, s tuffra ne$ âinani, ad ssirmen ttjaôa ur nepquccu"
  35,30,"Akken ad asen Ifk tiqvaâin nnsen, ad asen Irnu si lfevl iS. Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ippara tajmilt"
  35,31,"Ayen i k Nweêêa, si Tezmamt, d tidep id itebbten ayen ip id izwaren. Ih, Öebbi, $ef imdanen iS, Ippuxebbeô, Ipwali ten"
  35,32,"Sinna, Nerra d iweôôaten n Tezmamt, wid Nefren, ger imdanen nne£. Garasen, llan win idensen iman is, garasen alemmas, garasen win izeggwiren ar lxiô, s wannuf n Öebbi. Wagi d lfevl ameqwôan"
  35,33,"Loennet n Âaden, ara kecmen. Din, ad qqnen imeqyasen n ddheb, akked tyuqat. Leêrir, di lebsa nnsen"
  35,34,"Ad inin: \"cekôan i Öebbi i Issaferen fella$ le$wben. Ih, Mass nne$ Ipsemmiê, Ippara tajmilt"
  35,35,"I a$ Irran, s lefvl iS, axxam i tnezdu$t; ur a$ ipnal, degs, wugur; ur a$ ipnal, degs, âaggu"
  35,36,"I wid ijehlen, times n Loahennama. Ur tepfukku fellasen, ad mmten; ur ippifsus, fellasen, uâaqeb is. Akka, ay Nepqeîîi yal ajehli"
  35,37,"Degs, ad ppu$un: \"a Mass nne$! Ssuffe$ ane$, a nexdem ayen ilhan, maççi am akken nella nxeddem\"! Day ur awen Nesse$wzef ara laâmeô, akken a d immekti win id ismektayen? Iusa kwen id uneddaô. Ihi jeôôbet. I imednas, ur illi umâiwen"